Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戌时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了寻找突然失踪的奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一行人展开漫长的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家曾经一起\N度过好多次难关
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这次大家又要一起\N面对心灵的地狱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师加上珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:44.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:51.15,OP,,0,0,0,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.86,OP,,0,0,0,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:59.77,OP,,0,0,0,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:03.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:07.87,OP,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:16.30,OP,,0,0,0,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:21.67,OP,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:25.85,OP,,0,0,0,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.85,OP,,0,0,0,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:33.85,OP,,0,0,0,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.72,OP,,0,0,0,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.95,OP,,0,0,0,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:45.87,OP,,0,0,0,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:52.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:58.03,OP,,0,0,0,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:05.27,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在还找不到出口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵了  会分心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一早到现在都还没搞定\N马上就要天黑了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛抖个不停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师\N这座森林果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不会错了\N一定是妖怪的巢穴…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  又爆胎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种没用的废物  扔掉算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:03:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我妈买给我的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一股邪恶的气息…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座森林的主人\N差不多该现身了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会出现的会是鬼  还是蛇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪快点现身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么话快说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那边装模作样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点给我滚出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临我这座可悲的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第100话 真实的恶梦\N可悲的森林之役
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你看这妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  是蛾天丸同类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦?你们认得\N蛾天丸那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是我们族人的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说他跟一些\N低贱的人类狼狈为奸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后居然死在半妖的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这把刀还真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚说的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时那样的结果\N我还正觉得无趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有妖怪血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只死妖虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想帮蛾天丸报仇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天本大爷\N会很兴奋的奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮蛾天丸报仇?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别说笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种邪魔歪道  死了活该
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会理他那些闲事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱怎么说都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:06:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你们这些飞蛾死虫怪\N也一样没有好感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么呀\N啊  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太…太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直冲进身体里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力气…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐被吸走…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连铁碎牙也不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会吃人类的鲜血的\N是那些邪魔歪道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们全族的人\N一向吃的都是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐惧的心\N还有脆弱的灵魂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒  别被控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要坚强一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在再大声都没用  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们根本就听不见你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用等到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那些分身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会把他们的\N灵魂跟肉体吃个精光了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤…试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子只有打败这个妖怪\N才能解开法术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在连续不断的恶梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些隐藏在内心深处的\N恐惧跟绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都给我唤醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子连云母都比不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他应该还不能应付实战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒不这么认为  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得琥珀\N耍链条耍得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一琥珀有什么危险\N还有我跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  我好害怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了  姐姐在这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愉快  愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样出来散散心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那些什么痛苦烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就都把它忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦心师父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有看见\N我爸爸在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦心师父?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你亲生父亲告诉我\N恐怕要跟你来世再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来世再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候恐怕已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸…爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  爸爸\N我捡了这么多松果回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦  草太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蚋在里面耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有点怪怪的\N我觉得很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊  草太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股瘴气是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太  你快跑  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太  振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不可以过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续受苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受完苦之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有永无止尽的绝望\N等着你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地 慢慢地\N品尝那些恐怖的滋味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死妖怪\N你到底对他们做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过让他们做做梦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们做梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管人也好 妖怪也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐藏在内心深处的那种恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会借着梦境\N变得非常非常的具体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这些东西\N就是我们的饵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这死妖怪简直乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻放了戈薇他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  你这只半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出来\N你开始感到恐惧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不跟大家成群结队的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本是胆小又没用的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算剩下我一个\N我也照样能打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然拿我的同伴当成你的饵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不能忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那边逞英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最害怕最难忍受的恐惧\N我也会一并吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你还能威风多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招吧  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呸  光会用一张嘴说说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为这样就算赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我这条命没了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些不断帮我\N啃食他们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有肉体的分身\N全都会复活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就是你的死期了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等着成为\N你那些同伴的饵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也才有机会\N真正摆脱孤独的恐惧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫茧居然没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可恶了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于办到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人打败妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打败妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次爸爸一定会\N夸奖我做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是姐姐你的错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你没有夸奖我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦心师父  放了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那个风穴\N现在已经用到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后你哪里都去不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定把奈落找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只差一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:15:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们全都不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么会…\N我根本没打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师\N你就那么想帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了帮我\N牺牲同伴的性命也在所不惜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切全部都是你的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你对我爷爷\N下了这个风穴诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜啊  救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在上课的时候做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很少看到你上课打瞌睡耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚睡得还真熟哩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因为太过用功念书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为这种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续待在这里会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞刃血爪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的韧性跑到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会被梦境给侵蚀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是这么脆弱的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你就这样放弃自己的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要一个人\N自己去击败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候你可不要\N跟在后面哭哭啼啼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可以\N让那只飞蛾怪吃掉你的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一向都不是那么柔弱的女子\N不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒来命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令我坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  原谅姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这一辈子恐怕都没有机会\N回到我身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先杀了你\N然后跟你一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了从奈落手中把你抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这个办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对不能杀了琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要活着把他带回来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会给大家添麻烦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要再咯里罗唆的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正大家在一起就是比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你也满会打架的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙到底在怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再打开风穴的话\N我会先折断你这只手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要等到打败奈落\N风穴才能收起来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是裹足不前的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的一点都没错  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要撑下去  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:20:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  看不出来\N你真有两下子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…身上好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候在说什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在人类的样子\N打不过他的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会扔下你一个人跑掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  还有犬夜叉在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要还有犬夜叉在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那帮好朋友在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有再大的困难\N我们一定都能一起克服的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样才是我认识的你们嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马上可以\N离开这座森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出口就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为刚刚的一切\N都是蛾罗丸的幻术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:21:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害得我们无缘无故\N耽误了行程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有我在一旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.44,0:22:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们根本就软弱到不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.42,0:22:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么  有什么不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实  你说的并没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只限今天随便让你说说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.96,0:22:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么说是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了嘛  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都认同你够厉害\N不就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.80,0:22:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  这样我不接受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们真的认为\N是我救了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.44,0:22:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好歹跟我\N说一声“谢谢”才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样  戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就麻烦你\N代表大家说一句话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咿呀…你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒来命令我坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.29,0:22:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:22:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢  谢  你  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是过来叫我坐下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也该继续上路咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我肚子饿了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  戈薇\N刚刚你跟我说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.21,0:23:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.11,0:23:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没关系  再说一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你烦不烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  喂  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  我在叫你耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦  给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:34.15,ED,,0,0,0,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:43.95,ED,,0,0,0,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:53.22,ED,,0,0,0,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:24:03.22,ED,,0,0,0,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:08.20,ED,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:13.12,ED,,0,0,0,,活得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.12,0:24:20.52,ED,,0,0,0,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:27.07,ED,,0,0,0,,要默默承受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.07,0:24:31.25,ED,,0,0,0,,会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:38.50,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.95,0:24:48.52,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌才是我的路标
